  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients who are undergoing elective abdominal surgery after appropriate
             information of the study, and its possible risks that may arise therefrom and that at
             any time to refuse their cooperation, give a written consent to participate in the
             study.

          -  Patients who at the time of the interview have an ASA between 2 and 4.

          -  Patients with chronic kidney failure mild moderate (serum creatinine between 1.5 and
             3.0 mg / dl) can be included.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic kidney diseases with serum creatinine higher than 3.0 mg /DL

          -  Laparoscopic abdominal surgery

          -  ASA 1 and ASA 5 patients.

          -  Patients with cardiac insufficiency, ascites and respiratory insufficiency

          -  Diastolic hypertension &gt; 100 mmHg
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
